parameters: \nw[Grand]Why are there students in a place like this...

\nw[Taro]Ah, I only met her briefly... I don't know much
about her.

\nw[Grand]Well, never mind. Our current objective is the
<Conductor>. We can't afford to spend too much
time here.

\nw[Grand]If they seem troublesome, it's fine to neutralize
them first... Ami, what about the person in that
room? Do they seem to have high magical power?

\nw[Amy's voice]Yes? Is the person in that room near Grand and the
others?

\nw[Amy's voice]I can't detect any magical power. Are they really
there?

\nw[Taro](Come to think of it, when Kuno and the others
met, Uka said she couldn't sense their presence)

\nw[Amy's voice]Detection magic isn't foolproof, you know. There
might be some kind of trap or mechanism.

\nw[Finis]Is it Taro, Lumis's friend? I'm glad to see you're
doing well.
\nw[Taro]Ah, well, a lot of things happened...
\nw[Grand](Hey, do you know them? Investigate a little.)

\nw[Finis]I was in a bind because I was given a lot of tasks
that I'm not good at.
\nw[Taro]Oh, I see. So you're not one of the soldiers here?

\nw[Finis]Yeah, you're wrong. First of all, I don't look
like a soldier, do I?

\nw[Finis]...Well, whatever. Instead of wandering around
here, why don't you focus on your work?

\nw[Grand]Even though he looks normal, I didn't sense any
presence from him at all.

\nw[Grand]Amy, I was talking to him earlier, but can't you
still sense any magical power from him?

\nw[Amy's voice]I can't sense anything. It might be a magical
malfunction or something, I can't say for sure...

\nw[Taro]I understand that you're curious, but it's not the
time to be concerned about it, right?

\nw[Grand]Well, there was something that I've been curious
about from the start. The reason why the
<Conductor> came here is a mystery.

\nw[Taro]What's the point of worrying about something like
that?

\nw[Grand]There are few subordinates who bring them along,
and the soldiers here are not particularly
strong... In other words, they can be considered
as members of the information department.

\nw[Grand]In other words, it means that they don't want many
people to know. That's why they came here, because
they obtained that information...

\nw[Grand]Isn't he the one we're looking for? It's strange
that he's here in the first place, and it's also
odd that we can't sense any magical power from
him.

\nw[Grand]In other words, there is a possibility that they
are doing important work in the country of Misura.
There is also a high possibility that they are
connected to the <Conductor>.

\nw[Grand]If that's the case, we might as well catch them
here. Besides, if they're a woman, we might be
able to charm them.

\nw[Grand]Fortunately, it doesn't seem like they're on guard
here. It might be a good idea to restrain and
capture them here.

\nw[Taro]It's all just speculation and might not be
relevant at all. Don't you think we don't have
time for that?

\nw[Taro](He saved Kuno and the others from the <Eaters>,
so I can't let them do something like that to our
benefactor.)

\nw[Taro](Or rather, if they were able to stop the
<Eaters>, wouldn't that mean they're strong? I
won't tell them because it would make them even
more suspicious, but...)

\nw[Grand]Certainly, we want to achieve our goal quickly,
but if we capture this person here, it could also
be beneficial for Dios.
\nw[Taro](Damn, is it okay to just watch like this...?)

\nw[Finis]Hmm, according to this investigation result, it
seems to be overseas? But...

\nw[Grand](She hasn't noticed, let's restrain her like
this!)

\nw[Taro](Her movements weren't fast... Her attacks didn't
seem that strong... But...)
\nw[Grand]Damn it, if I can't capture you...!

\nw[Taro]Instant death... Even though she seemed quite
strong...

\nw[Finis]Please don't try to harm me, okay? I'll react to
it.

\nw[Taro](I wonder if we can communicate...? Fighting seems
impossible... So, should we run away?)

\nw[Finis]I wonder if it's better to put her to sleep? But
if I touch her, there's a high chance I'll end up
killing her...
\nw[Taro](Alright, let's run away. That's our only option!)

\nw[Taro](As I was paying attention to Finis, I didn't
notice that there was a soldier with a spear
waiting ahead to chase us.)

\nw[Taro](It seems like I was moving while on guard... I
can't breathe... It feels like something important
has been lost from my body, and I've lost my
strength.)

\nw[Finis]Um... I might die from this... I can't heal
myself, so someone...

\nw[Taro](To die here...? I don't want to... I don't want
to... No...)

\nw[Taro]Wait, this isn't the time for doing something like
this!
\nw[Grand]Hey, don't make a fuss! Tch, step back for now!

\nw[Grand]Damn it... Don't make a fuss next time we go,
okay?

\nw[Taro]Let's focus on achieving our goal first. We can
deal with that later, right?
\nw[Grand]Hmmm... That might be true as well...
